\s1 Prophecy Against the South  
\p
\v 45  The word of the \nd Lord\nd* came to me:  
\v 46 “Son of man, turn toward the south, and speak out against the south. Prophesy against the open scrub land of the Negev,  
\v 47  and say to the scrub land of the Negev, ‘Hear the word of the \nd Lord\nd*: This is what the sovereign \nd Lord\nd* says: Look here, I am about to start \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire in you, and it will devour every green tree and every dry tree in you. The flaming fire will not be extinguished, and the whole surface of the ground from the Negev to the north will be scorched by it.  
\v 48  And everyone will see that I, the \nd Lord\nd*, have burned it; it will not be extinguished.’”   
\p
\v 49  Then I said, “\w O|strong="H3068"\w* sovereign \nd Lord\nd*! They are saying of me, ‘Does he not simply speak in eloquent figures of speech?’”   
\c 21  
\p
\v 1  \w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w word|strong="H1697"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w came|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w*:  
\v 2 “\w Son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w*, \w turn|strong="H7760"\w* \w toward|strong="H1870"\w* Jerusalem \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w speak|strong="H5197"\w* \w out|strong="H6440"\w* \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* sanctuaries. \w Prophesy|strong="H5012"\w* \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w land|strong="H7704"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Israel  
\v 3  \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w say|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w This|strong="H3541"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w says|strong="H3541"\w*: \w Look|strong="H2005"\w*, \w I|strong="H2005"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* \w against|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*. \w I|strong="H2005"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* draw \w my|strong="H8085"\w* sword \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* sheath \w and|strong="H3068"\w* cut \w off|strong="H6440"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w both|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* righteous \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wicked.  
\v 4  \w Because|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* cut \w off|strong="H7200"\w* \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w both|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* righteous \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wicked, \w my|strong="H3605"\w* sword \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w go|strong="H3068"\w* \w out|strong="H3518"\w* \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* sheath \w against|strong="H3605"\w* \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w* \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* south \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* north.  
\v 5  \w Then|strong="H3808"\w* everyone \w will|strong="H3808"\w* know \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* am \w the|strong="H3069"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3069"\+w*\nd*, \w who|strong="H1931"\w* drew \w my|strong="H3808"\w* sword \w from|strong="H3808"\w* \w its|strong="H3808"\w* sheath – \w it|strong="H1931"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* sheathed again!’   
\p
\v 6 “\w And|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H1961"\w*, son \w of|strong="H3068"\w* man, groan \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w an|strong="H1961"\w* aching heart \w and|strong="H3068"\w* bitterness; groan \w before|strong="H1961"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* eyes.  
\v 7  \w When|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* ask \w you|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘Why \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* groaning?’ \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* reply, ‘\w Because|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* report \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w has|strong="H3478"\w* \w come|strong="H3478"\w*. \w Every|strong="H7760"\w* heart \w will|strong="H3478"\w* melt \w with|strong="H3389"\w* \w fear|strong="H6440"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w every|strong="H7760"\w* hand \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* limp; everyone \w will|strong="H3478"\w* faint \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w every|strong="H7760"\w* knee \w will|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* wet \w with|strong="H3389"\w* urine.’ \w Pay|strong="H7760"\w* \w attention|strong="H6440"\w* – \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w is|strong="H3478"\w* coming \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w it|strong="H7760"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* happen, declares \w the|strong="H6440"\w* sovereign \nd Lord\nd*.”   
\p
\v 8  \w The|strong="H3541"\w* word \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3541"\w* \nd \+w Lord|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w*:  
\v 9 “Son \w of|strong="H4480"\w* \w man|strong="H7563"\w*, prophesy \w and|strong="H2719"\w* say: ‘\w This|strong="H3651"\w* \w is|strong="H7563"\w* \w what|strong="H3651"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Lord|strong="H6662"\w* \w says|strong="H3282"\w*:  
\q1 “‘\w A|strong="H3068"\w* \w sword|strong="H2719"\w*, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w sword|strong="H2719"\w* \w is|strong="H7563"\w* sharpened,  
\q1 \w and|strong="H2719"\w* \w also|strong="H3318"\w* polished.   
\q1
\v 10  \w It|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* sharpened \w for|strong="H3588"\w* slaughter,  
\q1 \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* polished \w to|strong="H7725"\w* flash \w like|strong="H3318"\w* lightning!  
\p “‘\w Should|strong="H3068"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* rejoice \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* scepter \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* son? \w No|strong="H3808"\w*! \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w sword|strong="H2719"\w* despises \w every|strong="H3605"\w* tree!   
\q1
\v 11 “‘\w He|strong="H1121"\w* gave \w it|strong="H1121"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* polished,  
\q1 \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* grasped \w in|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5869"\w* hand –  
\q1 \w the|strong="H5869"\w* sword \w is|strong="H1121"\w* sharpened, \w it|strong="H1121"\w* \w is|strong="H1121"\w* polished –  
\q1 giving \w it|strong="H1121"\w* into \w the|strong="H5869"\w* hand \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5869"\w* executioner.   
\q1
\v 12  Cry \w out|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* moan, son \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w man|strong="H3605"\w*,  
\q1 \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w is|strong="H3820"\w* wielded \w against|strong="H5921"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H3820"\w*;  
\q1 \w against|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* princes \w of|strong="H3027"\w* Israel.  
